name: Cynthia Axne
content:
Since day one, I've been fighting to lower health care costs for Iowans.

The #BuildBackBetterAct:
✅ reduces prescription drug prices
✅ caps the cost of insulin
✅ lowers premiums
✅ expands Medicare coverage

all while CUTTING taxes for Iowa's middle class. #IA03 https://t.co/KdlL5BLFk4

name: Darren Soto
content:
